---
title: "Congratulations Vivienne, on your new paper published in Applied Energy!"
subtitle: "Energy system vulnerabilities in a zero-emission grid: The role of climate variability and technology uncertainty"
author: Lindsay Anderson
tags: news
category: papers
layout: post
---

Vivienne's new paper (with Vivek Srikrishnan, Kenji Doering, Elnaz Kabir, Scott Steinschneider) illuminates potential operational vulnerabilities of zero-emission grids under long-term scenarios. The paper also identifies key challenges to propose solutions that maintain reliability and achieve our clean energy objectives. The article appears in [Energy](https://doi.org/10.1016/j.energy.2025.137937). Congratulations Vivienne and team ! 
